freedays.app
Class FreeDaysRCMatch

java.lang.Object
  freedays.app.FreeDay
      freedays.app.FreeDaysRCMatch
Type Parameters:
T - represents the class to which the matching is restricted. It must extend FreeDay.
Direct Known Subclasses:
FreeDayC, FreeDayR
public abstract class FreeDaysRCMatch
extends FreeDay

Class used to extract the common behavior exhibited during the matching process of two objects matchable objects. Such objects need a complement to finalize.

Author:
fmacicasan
